## 6. Visual Aesthetic Requirements
* Maintain the crisp, white background with dark text.
* Keep fonts consistent (e.g., JetBrains Mono for tags/dates, standard legible font for titles and descriptions).
* Avoid box-shadows or rounded corners for a more brutalist, print-inspired layout.